<div class="friendfeed setup">
  
  <div class="form">
    <% form_tag(setup_confirm_path) do %>
      <h2>2. Enter your <%= link_to('FriendFeed.com', 'http://friendfeed.com/') %> Account</h2>
      <p><span>http://friendfeed.com/<%= text_field(:stream, :friendfeed_username, :class => '') %></span></p>
      <%= submit_tag('continue') %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div id="friendfeed_explanation" class="explanation">
    <h2>What the Hell is a FriendFeed?</h2>
    <p>FriendFeed is a cool service that aggregates all of your online activity. 
    Right now, Kakuteru uses that as it's backend. 
    We plan to support other lifestreaming services soon, but for now, you'll have to quickly create a FriendFeed account.</p>
    <p><%= button_to('get a FriendFeed account', 'http://friendfeed.com/') %></p> 
  </div>

</div>
